hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我摸摸下佢 佢都會咬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303db2ac919b22364f5f1918496cccaae0189818","tid":41731,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開門飲水我都明 係有時無啦啦望住我喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢想你去呵佢/陪佢玩<br />\n摸下巴<br />\n摸後腦<br />\n<br />\n我隻鳩貓成日向住我喵<br />\n我每次都去摸佢後腦<br />\n然後佢就會反肚<br />\n之後我摸佢下巴<br />\n佢就好似好舒服咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係摸多一分鐘之後<br />\n佢就會開始咬我隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n摸佢佢又走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我摸摸下佢 佢都會咬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/170533_3083787fb5ee4cdd40395706e3c4acfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F170533_3083787fb5ee4cdd40395706e3c4acfb.jpg&h=29ac4d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b14e4afe7e075d3e8e91cc4010b2738c7bb211f7","tid":41731,"uid":12039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好想<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同是天涯淪落人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}